## 🛠️ Quick Start
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/dionisiou27/truthshield-api.git

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Set up environment
cp .env.example .env
# Add your API keys

# Run development server
uvicorn src.api.main:app --reload
